commit.message:
Don't unveil(2) local (sender) files any more: the first call will make
subsequent access fail.
Import from OpenBSD.  Tweak to remove mmap header and spurrious assert.
Guard for sys/queue.h.  Found when testing on a musl Linux.
On SunOS, "ERR" is an obscure macro already.  Don't let it through.
major() and mino() need sys/mkdev.h on SunOS.
